# OpenAI API Integration (Cognitive Layer)

This module establishes Xenith's foundational AI reasoning capabilities using OpenAI's GPT model.

---

## Purpose

- Handle natural language understanding and generation
- Enable voice-to-text and text-to-speech interaction loops
- Support recursive symbolic reasoning (future extension)

---

